## Temporalize

Project developed on RPG Maker XP, based on the Pokémon Starter Development Kit. All the content here is subject to change and enrichment during the development of the project. First of all, I would like to thank all the people involved in the project, be it the Creators, members of various communities such as Pokémon Workshop, or yourself. For all the support given, without which the project would never have been able to move forward, I have to say to all of you...

"Thank you! "

