## Synopsis

For centuries, a rumor has spread throughout the Yron region. It speaks of a ritual to summon the Time Master Pokémon. Many people have been searching for the artifacts to perform this ritual. Erwin Blue, a businessman and head of the Temporis Corporation, has found something that brings him as close as possible to this goal: a lead to the artifacts. You play as a 14 year old protagonist. Professor Wollend gives you your first Pokémon as part of the "Pokédex" program. Along the way, you will follow in the footsteps of your older brother Rio, the current master of the Yron Region League. However, it won't be that easy, as you'll have to deal with the Temporis Corporation, which will stand in your way.

